{"id": "art-1371", "label": "Art. 1371", "title": "Art. 1371", "slug": "art-1371", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1729122104\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2256\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1729122104\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 137<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_690328834\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2255\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_690328834\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii sunt <span class=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span>\nde c&#259;tre adunarea general&#259; ordinar&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>,\ncu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> primilor administratori, care sunt <span\nclass=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span> prin actul constitutiv.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_862022662\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2254\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_862022662\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Candida&#355;ii</span> pentru\nposturile de administrator sunt <span class=SpellE>nominaliza&#355;i</span> de\nc&#259;tre membrii actuali ai consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\nsau de c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_944084036\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2253\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_944084036\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Pe durata îndeplinirii mandatului, administratorii nu\npot încheia cu societatea un contract de munc&#259;. În cazul în care\nadministratorii au fost <span class=SpellE>desemna&#355;i</span> dintre <span\nclass=SpellE>salaria&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ncontractul individual de munc&#259; este suspendat pe perioada mandatului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1877943672\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2252\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1877943672\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Administratorii pot fi <span class=SpellE>revoca&#355;i</span>\noricând de c&#259;tre adunarea general&#259; ordinar&#259; a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>. În cazul în care revocarea survine\nf&#259;r&#259; just&#259; cauz&#259;, administratorul este <span class=SpellE>îndrept&#259;&#355;it</span>\nla plata unor daune-interese.</span></p>"}